  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age between 20-50 years;

          -  BMI between 28-36 kg/m2;

          -  Weight stabile 3 months prior to the study inclusion;

          -  Less than 10 hours of weekly exercise

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Diabetes

          -  Allergic to phenylalanine or milk

          -  Smoking

          -  Pregnancy or breast-feeding
      </textblock>
